  "texts": [
    "The model was run on a PHI-compliant virtual machine with 8xNVIDIA L4 24GB GPUs.",
    "Given the 512 context window limit of Flan-T5, we used prompts of fewer than 20 tokens and chunked input text to under 100 tokens with a 15-token stride.",
    "We used four distinct prompts, and the output-named entities from each prompt were aggregated and deduplicated to form the final list of entities.",
    "Illustrations of each prompt type are provided in Supplementary Fig. 2.",
    "Our approach leverages NER prompts to capture all clinically named entities; however, users have the ability to craft more focused NER prompts (e.g., \"Return all named entities related to congestive heart failure\")."
  ],
